reviewtext: I have a bunch of cables, from low to mid-end.I would rate them somewhere in the middle between the low end and the mid end in terms of audio quality.The connectors are a royal pain. They are WAY TOO TIGHT which makes them very hard to plug in and even worse when its time to unplug them - they are so tight to a point one can damage the RCA jack on the equipment.I wish I had kept the package otherwise these would be back for return in no time.
summary: over-hyped, pain in the rear connectors, pointless
